{
  "3246190": {
    "name": "关于我们尝试把似曾相见的「那些游戏」做得更加刺激，却惊觉火柴人存在极限这档事。",
    "steam_appid": 3246190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/bc82d429177fbd1c83a90c69703e9167.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变得更加「有难度」、「有乐趣」的“那些游戏”又回来了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在更加困难的关卡中，再次畅玩“那些游戏”1、2的小游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次的小游戏合集比以往更具挑战性，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可从中获得更多的爽快感和成就感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=290 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/740a353b5cab21501909b1138a77982b.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次推出的“那些游戏激”，不仅有着更高的难度，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人或受到攻击时的特效也更为激烈，表现更为丰富！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各类小游戏还增加了新的玩法，等你来发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/abd4ce0d894bde43d5de620e551eb8a9.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内含“那些游戏”系列小游戏「拔插销」「数字塔」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「分颜色」「反弹射手」「画线自保」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而「迷人滚动区」也将全面升级为「生存滚动区」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为更具难度的全新游戏登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.poster.avif?t=1769670427\" width=296 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.webm?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246190/extras/0fe9523644b2cf040e7fdb30f8a0aa19.mp4?t=1769670427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“那些游戏”系列最具难度的“那些游戏激”，你究竟能否通关呢！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·似曾相识的“那些游戏”升级为「极限」又回来了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·本作的小游戏不仅提高了难度，外观和特效也进一步升级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·在可以畅玩“那些游戏”的「游玩小游戏」中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　包含6种小游戏，共计155个关卡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·通过“那些游戏”与全国玩家比拼的「挑战排名」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·使用硬币获得名牌与称号的「扭蛋」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·使用名牌与称号制作自己专属名牌的「自定义名牌」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·能够查看全国玩家当月排名的“最新排名”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·完成各种任务条件获得报酬的「任务」功能也丰富多彩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※本作中部分教程关卡沿用已发售的「那些游戏」「那些游戏2」的关卡。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“那些游戏”系列的高手玩家可跳过教程，直接游玩本作新关卡！当然，您也可以从头体验所有关卡！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各类小游戏都有对应的教程，方便“那些游戏”系列的新玩家快速上手。</strong></p>",
